data.description: The All American Home!!! This beautiful home was built using all American made products situated on 2.10 acres in Jones County with porches, decks, an above ground pool for entertaining! Come inside and be wowed by the open spacious living area with built-ins, gorgeous rock fireplace kitchen is open to living area with granite countertops, custom cabinets and so much more! The outside building is planned for an in-law suite.
